archimate:BusinessObject.name: EIRA Viewpoint
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation:
DESCRIPTION: The EIRA© provides several viewpoints (1) that conform to EIRA© views. The viewpoints provide a perspective with specific stakeholders concern in mind.
(1) A specification of the conventions for a particular kind of architecture view. Source: TOGAF https://pubs.opengroup.org/architecture/togaf9-doc/arch/chap03.html#tag_03_18
